
124th days.

2021.04.19(Monday).


How's your new job going?

새로 들어간 회사는 어때?


Well, I think it's a very special company.

음 굉장히 특별한 회사인 것 같아.


What do you mean?

무슨 뜻이야?


I work at the office during the first and second week of every month.

매달 첫째, 둘째 주는 사무실에서 근무해.

And then I have to work at home during the third and fourth weeks.

그리고서 셋째, 넷째주는 집에서 근무해야 해.


Wow, that doesn't sound very stable.

와, 별로 안정감이 없게 들리는데?


Yes, I can't get used to any patterns.

음, 어떤 패턴에도 적응할 수가 없어.


I've never heard of that type of work.

그런 근무 형태는 한 번도 들어본 적 없어.


The new atmosphere is good on the other hand.

새로운 분위기라 한 편으론 좋아.

Everything's new.

